{
  "title": "Mouthwatering Savory Tunisian Lamb Tagine",
  "description": "A savory and juicy Tunisian dish featuring lamb, colatura, and infuse oil, perfect for a hangover cure. This egg free friendly recipe is a must try for any food lover.",
  "cuisine": "Tunisian",
